<figureCitation captionStart="Fig. 7" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Fig. 7. Abdominal apex of female Burttia caerulea sp. nov. A. semilateral; B. lateral; C. semilateral view." figureDoi="10.3897/jor.31.70565.fig7" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/638410" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">7B, C</figureCitation>
